name: Paralog-tools
tagline: Tools to work with Paralog database
body:
Paralog tools
=============

Paralog tools enable you to work with Paralog database without having to install Paralog on your machine. For now, it contains some tools to import NMEA183 and Flysight files to database, generate rudimentary website from the database.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
